description: A new adventure beckons for the Warrior of Light within the latest expansion for Final Fantasy XIV. This 5th expansion entitled Dawntrail brings with it an epic new story set on a brand new continent teeming with exciting new gameplay opportunities. But what exactly can we expect from this latest expansion? Well, this is everything you need to know about Final Fantasy XIV: Dawntrail.
title: Everything You Need to Know | Final Fantasy XIV Dawntrail
